{"tid":1105260,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］有冇人同我一樣 係會悶到嘔？","createTime":"2019-04-13T17:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T12:01:13.000Z","uid":68851,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c132dc867854ef662a3affd0b23598e8030890","tid":1105260,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"由中學開始 到而家<br />\n一玩啲咩槍game 初初玩冇嘢<br />\n一排之後就不停作嘔<br />\n但我唔係對血敏感 因為玩第啲有血嘅作品完全冇事<br />\n就算隻槍game冇血 都會作嘔<br />\n<br />\n另外太悶都會 所以硬係要搵啲嘢做下咁？<br />\n好有鬱悶嘅感覺 跟住就係咁作嘔 <br />\n<br />\n食住糖可以暫時冇作嘔 但食完又恢復返不停作嘔<br />\n真真正正悶到嘔 可以點算？<br />\n<br />\nGoogle過 搵唔到啲咩資料<br />\n就算睇醫生 可以去咩專科睇？"},{"pid":"d5ce2812b62c89c17cbb4410979cb8c383204857","tid":1105260,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"負評係咩心態？<br />\n認真想問下有冇人都係咁<br />\n即係唔舒服都唔啱咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795d0031c4ced416ceb73c29e0559482cf818e24","tid":1105260,"uid":101253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"睇心理醫生好過上黎問"},{"pid":"371c38edc2e82695d72366cb5bfd6e73188ceddb","tid":1105260,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795d0031c4ced416ceb73c29e0559482cf818e24","tid":1105260,"uid":101253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"睇心理醫生好過上黎問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"就係唔知心理定生理問題<br />\n唔知睇咩科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf4839662c19cee80e210d5d6b62fe84b771f92","tid":1105260,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371c38edc2e82695d72366cb5bfd6e73188ceddb","tid":1105260,"uid":68851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795d0031c4ced416ceb73c29e0559482cf818e24","tid":1105260,"uid":101253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"睇心理醫生好過上黎問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:46: